a-formation" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Agenda Formation</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/governance-contributions/conflict-resolution" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Conflict Resolution</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/governance-contributions/decision-making" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Decision-Making</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-interdependency field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Interdependency	:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/interdependency/4-often-interdependent-other-issues" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">4 - Often Interdependent with Other Issues</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-influence-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Kind of Influence:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/kind-influence/consultation-ie-advise-decision-makers" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Consultation (i.e. to advise decision makers)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitated field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facilitated:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Yes</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Typical Sponsoring Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/entities/government-owned-corporation" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Government-Owned Corporation</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-implementing-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div cla